% B6b -- raiseerror with a deeper estack.
% Each nested proc call adds a frame to the estack before the
% error fires. The estack snapshot in raiseerror (recordstacks=true)
% scales linearly with this depth.
/d4 { /test /Bench raiseerror } def
/d3 { d4 } def
/d2 { d3 } def
/d1 { d2 } def
tic 1000000 { { d1 } stopped { handleerror } if } repeat toc ==
quit
